We’re listening.

00:55:02.349 --> 00:55:04.517 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“To the Governing Body.

00:55:04.517 --> 00:55:08.555 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Dear Brothers: Over 2,500 years ago,

00:55:08.555 --> 00:55:11.358 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Jehovah addressed Jeremiah with the words:

00:55:11.358 --> 00:55:15.295 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“‘Here I am, Jehovah, the God of all mankind.

00:55:15.295 --> 00:55:18.298 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Is there anything too wonderful for me?’

00:55:19.799 --> 00:55:22.202 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Attending Gilead at this time in our lives

00:55:22.202 --> 00:55:26.106 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“and in the midst of a pandemic
seemed too wonderful to us.

00:55:26.106 --> 00:55:29.242 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“But it was not too wonderful for Jehovah.

00:55:29.242 --> 00:55:31.544 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Thank you for the undeserved kindness

00:55:31.544 --> 00:55:35.415 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“of being invited
to attend this unique school.

00:55:35.415 --> 00:55:37.517 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“The pinnacle of education

00:55:37.517 --> 00:55:40.487 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“in this world is divine education.

00:55:40.487 --> 00:55:43.056 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Through it, the depth of God’s wisdom

00:55:43.056 --> 00:55:45.258 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“has taken on new meaning for us.

00:55:45.258 --> 00:55:49.562 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We feel a greater closeness
to Jehovah than ever before.

00:55:49.562 --> 00:55:53.099 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“And we feel a closeness to our legacy

00:55:53.099 --> 00:55:56.703 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“—from Adam
to the ‘faithful and discreet slave.’

00:55:56.703 --> 00:55:59.439 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“At the same time, Gilead has revealed ways

00:55:59.439 --> 00:56:02.409 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“in which we need
to continue to grow spiritually

00:56:02.409 --> 00:56:06.613 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“while providing the blueprint
and the motivation to do so.

00:56:07.947 --> 00:56:10.016 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We love our dear instructors

00:56:10.016 --> 00:56:14.387 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“who brought out of their ‘treasure store
things both new and old’

00:56:14.387 --> 00:56:17.157 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“as they journeyed
with us through God’s Word.

00:56:17.157 --> 00:56:19.426 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Their example and that of their wives

00:56:19.426 --> 00:56:22.062 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“helped us during these
five months of molding.

00:56:22.062 --> 00:56:26.866 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“And yet, by the way
the Scriptures were opened up

00:56:26.866 --> 00:56:30.837 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“and spiritual matters
were explained by spiritual words,

00:56:30.837 --> 00:56:33.339 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“we could feel
that we were really being taught

00:56:33.339 --> 00:56:37.644 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“by our ‘Grand Instructor,’ Jehovah,
and our Exemplar, Jesus.

00:56:39.045 --> 00:56:41.414 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Thank you too for taking precious time

00:56:41.414 --> 00:56:44.984 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“from your busy schedules
to deliver lectures to us.

00:56:44.984 --> 00:56:49.389 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Each one of you, as well as all
of those assigned to give lectures, 

00:56:49.389 --> 00:56:54.394 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“delivered information to us
with warmth and enthusiasm.

00:56:54.394 --> 00:56:58.998 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We saw Bible truth
so much simpler and more clearly.

00:56:58.998 --> 00:57:02.969 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Your humility, sense of humor, and kindness

00:57:02.969 --> 00:57:05.371 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“showed your tender affection for us.

00:57:05.371 --> 00:57:07.841 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Like Paul, you were determined to impart

00:57:07.841 --> 00:57:12.645 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“not only the good news of God
but also your very selves.

00:57:12.645 --> 00:57:16.516 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We will never forget your love for Jehovah

00:57:16.516 --> 00:57:19.686 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“and the privilege we have had
to learn from you in person.

00:57:20.887 --> 00:57:24.090 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We also feel a deep debt of gratitude

00:57:24.090 --> 00:57:26.893 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“to the Bethel family
for their living examples

00:57:26.893 --> 00:57:29.462 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“of kindness and hospitality

00:57:29.462 --> 00:57:32.899 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“—qualities we learn so much about in class.

