“Even routine trips to the pantry
or a walk around the complex

00:57:36.803 --> 00:57:40.540 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“turned into spontaneous
interchanges of encouragement.

00:57:40.540 --> 00:57:43.610 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“For this, we consider
the Bethel family’s example

00:57:43.610 --> 00:57:45.612 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“to be part of our education.

00:57:47.280 --> 00:57:50.116 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We know what we have to do now

00:57:50.116 --> 00:57:54.320 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“—apply ourselves
to strengthening and stabilizing

00:57:54.320 --> 00:57:58.324 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“by upholding Bible truth
and caring for Jehovah’s precious sheep

00:57:58.324 --> 00:58:00.927 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“in the areas where we will serve.

00:58:00.927 --> 00:58:03.663 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“This is a humbling assignment,

00:58:03.663 --> 00:58:06.633 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“but it is one that we want to carry out

00:58:06.633 --> 00:58:10.203 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“by imitating your example
and that of the Christ.

00:58:10.203 --> 00:58:14.407 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“We are fully confident
that Jehovah will help us

00:58:14.407 --> 00:58:18.745 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“because we have seen
that nothing is too wonderful for him.

00:58:18.745 --> 00:58:21.714 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“With warm love, your Brothers and Sisters,

00:58:21.714 --> 00:58:24.384 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
150th class of Gilead.”

00:58:39.199 --> 00:58:41.501 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Ryan didn’t want to hug me.

00:58:42.969 --> 00:58:45.305 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s personal, you know?

00:58:49.075 --> 00:58:52.579 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, those are very touching sentiments,

00:58:52.579 --> 00:58:57.417 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and the Governing Body treasures
those expressions from all of you.

00:58:57.417 --> 00:59:00.420 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Just some concluding comments for you,

00:59:00.420 --> 00:59:03.723 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
some things to pass on that, of course,

00:59:03.723 --> 00:59:05.725 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
all of us listening can benefit from.

00:59:05.725 --> 00:59:10.163 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We mentioned we’d talk about the SKE

00:59:10.163 --> 00:59:12.865 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
(School for Kingdom Evangelizers),

00:59:12.865 --> 00:59:15.201 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and, see, everything changed with Gilead.

00:59:15.201 --> 00:59:18.738 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
We’ll give you some statistics shortly.

00:59:18.738 --> 00:59:22.508 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The School for Kingdom Evangelizers

00:59:22.508 --> 00:59:25.712 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
has just been so blessed by Jehovah.

00:59:25.712 --> 00:59:30.717 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Only two months,
but they are just strengthening

00:59:30.717 --> 00:59:33.052 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the brothers and sisters in the field.

00:59:33.052 --> 00:59:36.022 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Some of them end up
in the circuit work or as missionaries.

00:59:36.022 --> 00:59:38.291 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So He’s blessing that.

00:59:38.291 --> 00:59:43.296 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And what is another blessing is that
as we deal with this side of Armageddon

00:59:43.296 --> 00:59:45.999 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
(all these different languages),

00:59:45.999 --> 00:59:50.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
they don’t have to learn English,
which was always a struggle.

00:59:50.270 --> 00:59:54.040 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That’s the fault of language

00:59:54.040 --> 00:59:57.176 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but certainly not
of those sincere individuals

00:59:57.176 --> 00:59:59.979 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
wanting to come to Gilead.

00:59:59.979 --> 01:00:02.115 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So they’ve done wonderfully.

01:00:02.115 --> 01:00:03.950 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah has blessed the school.

01:00:03.950 --> 01:00:06.753 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, you’ve had these five months,

01:00:06.753 --> 01:00:11.758 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and these are some statistics
that reveal how Jehovah has blessed

01:00:11.758 --> 01:00:15.061 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the Governing Body’s decision years ago.

01:00:15.061 --> 01:00:17.130 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Because, you know, Gilead has changed.

01:00:17.130 --> 01:00:20.266 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You see some of the history
and appreciate it very much

01:00:20.266 --> 01:00:24.304 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—Brother Jackson’s review
of some of these pictures.

01:00:24.304 --> 01:00:27.340 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But it was a missionary school, obviously,

01:00:27.340 --> 01:00:30.643 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it did tremendous work
after World War II.

01:00:30.643 --> 01:00:33.379 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But you may remember

01:00:33.379 --> 01:00:35.381 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
(these are statistics

01:00:35.381 --> 01:00:39.952 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
starting with class 132, October 2011)

01:00:39.952 --> 01:00:43.389 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that the focus of the school changed.

01:00:43.389 --> 01:00:47.694 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
See, now He brought in
special full-time servants.

01:00:47.694 --> 01:00:49.696 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So there was a time
that you could go to Gilead

01:00:49.696 --> 01:00:53.633 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
if you were a regular pioneer
and you had good recommendations.

01:00:53.633 --> 01:00:57.270 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But these were all
special full-time servants.

01:00:57.270 --> 01:01:01.574 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
What was the thinking behind the decision?

01:01:01.574 --> 01:01:04.510 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It was to stabilize and strengthen

01:01:04.510 --> 01:01:06.946 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the field and branch organization

01:01:09.048 --> 01:01:12.752 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to help the brothers there in the branches

01:01:12.752 --> 01:01:15.855 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that they serve in to be sure to adhere

01:01:15.855 --> 01:01:18.458 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to Scriptural and theocratic direction.

01:01:18.458 --> 01:01:21.661 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So the school has really been blessed

01:01:21.661 --> 01:01:26.432 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
by the decision that Jehovah
helped the Governing Body to make.

01:01:26.432 --> 01:01:28.434 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And it’s his organization

01:01:28.434 --> 01:01:31.404 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—this earthly part,
and it’s just been amazing

01:01:31.404 --> 01:01:34.741 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
with what has happened to show the results:

01:01:34.741 --> 01:01:38.111 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Wisdom is proved righteous
by its works [or results].”

01:01:38.111 --> 01:01:40.246 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So here are some statistics:

01:01:41.114 --> 01:01:44.016 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There are 675 Branch

01:01:44.016 --> 01:01:47.787 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and 17 Country Committee
members worldwide.

01:01:47.787 --> 01:01:51.023 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So that’s 692.

01:01:51.023 --> 01:01:54.660 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Of these 692 members,

01:01:54.660 --> 01:01:58.464 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
355 are Gilead graduates.

01:02:00.133 --> 01:02:04.570 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So you’re talking about 51.3 percent already

01:02:04.570 --> 01:02:07.039 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
since we started that.

01:02:07.039 --> 01:02:10.443 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, of the 355 graduates,

01:02:10.443 --> 01:02:13.713 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
221 of them (which is 62 percent)

01:02:13.713 --> 01:02:17.583 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
are from classes 132 to 149.

01:02:17.583 --> 01:02:20.586 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
This is in these last ten years.

01:02:20.586 --> 01:02:23.856 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So these 221 brothers

01:02:23.856 --> 01:02:26.659 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
represent 46.2 percent

01:02:26.659 --> 01:02:30.496 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of the 478 total brothers
who are graduates

01:02:30.496 --> 01:02:33.566 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
of classes 132-149.

01:02:34.634 --> 01:02:39.305 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
And what happens, too,
is that now we have some of you here

01:02:39.305 --> 01:02:42.308 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
who are already going to be
on Branch Committees.

01:02:42.308 --> 01:02:44.510 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
That happened in past classes too,

01:02:44.510 --> 01:02:47.613 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
but some of them
who went to their assignments

01:02:47.613 --> 01:02:50.183 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
weren’t on their committees right away.

01:02:50.183 --> 01:02:52.752 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
But not too long after (some years),

01:02:52.752 --> 01:02:54.754 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
they’re on the committees.

01:02:54.754 --> 01:02:58.624 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So Gilead made a big difference for them,

01:02:58.624 --> 01:03:01.327 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and it’s helping the organization.

01:03:01.327 --> 01:03:03.429 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
They’ve been around headquarters,

01:03:03.429 --> 01:03:05.531 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
like I’ve told classes in the past,

01:03:05.531 --> 01:03:09.535 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
even though they’re way
on the other side of the planet.

01:03:09.535 --> 01:03:13.439 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You just can’t make that appear in a video.

01:03:13.439 --> 01:03:17.510 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s not like being here
and receiving that education.

01:03:17.510 --> 01:03:20.813 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So the numbers have gone up now,

01:03:20.813 --> 01:03:24.083 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and there are more of you
on Branch Committees.

01:03:24.083 --> 01:03:26.953 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Others will take Jehovah’s training

01:03:26.953 --> 01:03:31.090 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and offer themselves
and strengthen as they can.

01:03:31.090 --> 01:03:33.092 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So good results

01:03:33.092 --> 01:03:36.229 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—Jehovah gets all the praise and glory.

01:03:36.229 --> 01:03:39.198 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Gilead has been a blessing

01:03:39.198 --> 01:03:43.469 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to the earthly part
of Jehovah’s organization.

01:03:43.469 --> 01:03:48.508 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, finally, just these
brief comments for you

01:03:48.508 --> 01:03:50.977 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—very brief.

01:03:50.977 --> 01:03:54.614 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
At the graduation, the 52nd class,

01:03:55.848 --> 01:04:00.052 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Brother Knorr stressed the need
for the graduates to be humble.

01:04:00.052 --> 01:04:03.890 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Now, you’ve heard that
quite a few times during class,

01:04:05.124 --> 01:04:08.528 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and they intensified this
toward the last couple of weeks

01:04:08.528 --> 01:04:12.031 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
if I know these instructors
like I think I do.

01:04:12.031 --> 01:04:16.502 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
“Be lowly in mind when you’re teaching
others,” Brother Knorr told them.

01:04:16.502 --> 01:04:20.840 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You can’t overemphasize being humble

01:04:20.840 --> 01:04:23.409 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
—you just can’t overemphasize it.

01:04:23.409 --> 01:04:27.179 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s crucial for Jehovah
to use us continually,

01:04:27.179 --> 01:04:29.015 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and we believe

01:04:29.015 --> 01:04:32.652 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that same message
goes for you in class 150

01:04:32.652 --> 01:04:35.755 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
that Brother Knorr gave class 52.

01:04:35.755 --> 01:04:36.956 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Be humble.

01:04:36.956 --> 01:04:40.159 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Teach others with a lowliness of mind.

01:04:42.728 --> 01:04:46.332 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So you humbly rendering
your sacred service

01:04:46.332 --> 01:04:48.367 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to Jehovah God

01:04:48.367 --> 01:04:52.805 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
is going to cause
your heavenly Father to rejoice.

01:04:53.940 --> 01:04:57.610 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So cause him to rejoice,
and we know you will.

